DOC.brief_title: Phase I Multiple Ascending Dose Study for AZD 7268 in Healthy Volunteers
DOC.criteria: Provision of Informed Consent Healthy male subjects and female subjects (of nonchild bearing potential) with suitable veins for cannulation or repeated venipuncture Inability to understand or cooperate with given information Any positive result on screening for human immune deficiency virus (HIV), Hepatitis B, or Hepatitis C test History of seizure (including infancy febrile seizures) or family history of seizure
